2010/05/barbecue-bob-in-fishtown.php">Barbecue Bob In Fishtown<br />Glenn Jones</a></h4><p>ギタリスト「Glenn Jones」の作品。リラクゼーションスペースで流れてほしい音楽です。ギターのみでの演奏ですが心地よく爽やかな気分になれる極上の癒しの音楽。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002JCYSRS?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002JCYSRS" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Barbecue Bob In Fishtown-Glenn Jones']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/stat?id=k5eaLrmqXSs&offerid=94348&type=3&subid=0&tmpid=2192&RD_PARM1=http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fkeep-it-a-hundred-years%252Fid325763317%253Fi%253D325764690%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Barbecue Bob In Fishtown-Glenn Jones']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/hello-sir-records-split-ep.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/maserati.jpg" alt="Hello Sir Records Split EP / Cinemechanica + Maserati + We Versus The Shark" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/hello-sir-records-split-ep.php">Hello Sir Records Split EP<br />Cinemechanica + Maserati + We Versus The Shark</a></h4><p>一転して激しいサウンドです。勢いがあり、ビート感を感じられるポストロック作品。流れるような軽快なギターサウンドを聴いて夜の世界に浸りましょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00073G4FK?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00073G4FK" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Hello Sir Records Split EP-Cinemechanica + Maserati + We Versus The Shark']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/stat?id=k5eaLrmqXSs&offerid=94348&type=3&subid=0&tmpid=2192&RD_PARM1=http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fsee-carolinas-fastest-trees%252Fid74283273%253Fi%253D74283168%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Hello Sir Records Split EP-Cinemechanica + Maserati + We Versus The Shark']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/luminary.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/luminary.jpg" alt="Luminary / Hadoken" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/luminary.php">Luminary<br />Hadoken</a></h4><p>続いて再びポストロック作品。Tortoiseのような小刻みなギターと暗く静かなサウンドが同居していて心地よい作品です。お酒を飲みながら聴きたくなる作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003A9I7PS?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003A9I7PS" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Luminary-Hadoken']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/stat?id=k5eaLrmqXSs&offerid=94348&type=3&subid=0&tmpid=2192&RD_PARM1=http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fprelude%252Fid362173331%253Fi%253D362173344%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTISTNAME: Had" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Luminary-Hadoken']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/butterfly-horse-street.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/butterflyhorsestreet.jpg" alt="Butterfly Horse Street / Hisato Higuchi" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/butterfly-horse-street.php">Butterfly Horse Street<br />Hisato Higuchi</a></h4><p>ノイズなのかメロディなのか曖昧なサウンドが特徴のアルバム。米Wire誌で注目された「樋口寿人」が奏でる音に夜の空間作りを任せてみるのもいいでしょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000WCN8YQ?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000WCN8YQ" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Butterfly Horse Street-Hisato Higuchi']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/stat?id=k5eaLrmqXSs&offerid=94348&type=3&subid=0&tmpid=2192&RD_PARM1=http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fmelody-in-the-mud%252Fid267025605%253Fi%253D267026033%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTIS" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Butterfly Horse Street-Hisato Higuchi']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

